{"tid":2081454,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【勵志】科大數學系獲9所企業聘書","createTime":"2020-06-27T08:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T16:36:56.000Z","uid":225931,"like":9,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6c754ae1624a05428a3666412fce8a0aaf3d9709","tid":2081454,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3917146/org/a0b4a6d2f139600c809c6ed711c2b89b.jpg/TQTUGzve3uox_6bKP6TSVa_f6iyMKzSfq1XnRqtV50Y?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3917146%2Forg%2Fa0b4a6d2f139600c809c6ed711c2b89b.jpg%2FTQTUGzve3uox_6bKP6TSVa_f6iyMKzSfq1XnRqtV50Y%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=754e75eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年畢業於科大理學院數學系的周冠達，在一間跨國快速消費品企業擔任銷售經理，談及畢業生面對前程，他認為同學在大學初期應盡早規劃未來，參加大量課餘活動，讓履歷表不致一片空白。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，他的「計劃」並不如此，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">性格外向</span>，相比勤奮好學的同學，他在大學的生活充滿了「瘋狂體驗和驚險刺激」，與其只對着課本，他會到台灣環島單車遊；大學一年級時，參加賽嘗試pitching換「免費搭車」；他亦專程到日本學習秘傳蛋包飯等；直至大學三年級的暑假，他終於開始擔心將來的就業，於是報讀牛津大學的英文班，期間得到教授的青睞，邀請他延長留校的時間聽課；同時亦在成都經貿辦實習，研究港人在當地創業的優惠措施。<br />\n<br />\n因以上情況周冠達的GPA不足3.3，未能符合跨國公司招聘的最低要求，為此他先在履歷表填上「期望或預期成績」為GPA3.3，獲得面試機會才如實坦告成績，並仗賴豐富的大學經驗吸引面試官。周冠達自嘲︰「諗返起當時搵工仲勤力過我讀書。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/424819/%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9Fgpa%E6%9C%AA%E5%A4%A0%E5%88%86%E5%8D%BB%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%979%E6%89%80%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E8%81%98%E6%9B%B8-%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD-%E9%9B%A3%E9%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E8%BF%8E%E5%88%83%E8%80%8C%E8%A7%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F424819%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259Fgpa%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%258D%25BB%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25BE%25979%25E6%2589%2580%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%2581%2598%25E6%259B%25B8-%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25A5%25BD-%25E9%259B%25A3%25E9%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25BF%258E%25E5%2588%2583%25E8%2580%258C%25E8%25A7%25A3&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=638db706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/424819/%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9Fgpa%E6%9C%AA%E5%A4%A0%E5%88%86%E5%8D%BB%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%979%E6%89%80%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E8%81%98%E6%9B%B8-%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD-%E9%9B%A3%E9%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E8%BF%8E%E5%88%83%E8%80%8C%E8%A7%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090ab94631711baaac01b3755016610ef889a195","tid":2081454,"uid":47659,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"支共01 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca75e7bb80b3d29b96e28daa5136bdad6bc30848","tid":2081454,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"讀數可以有咁多人請咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fa5c916a131db32c0643569620c8e445280503","tid":2081454,"uid":85629,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"同時亦在成都經貿辦實習，研究港人在當地創業的優惠措施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e5aa7a6d6eb7371fddd42f7aaa509180baca65","tid":2081454,"uid":144843,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3d1299e79488de377c25e853811ad09edddfa25","tid":2081454,"uid":7333,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"咁究竟係外向定內向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39ece0d05de